"title": "6624: confession, of sin",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6624: confession, of sin",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An admission of sin on the part of individuals or groups of people. Genuine repentance and confession herald divine forgiveness.</p>\n<h2>Confession of sin leads to divine forgiveness</h2>\n<h3>Under the old covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:13\">PRO 28:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:21\">LEV 16:21</a> <em>Part of the ritual of the Day of Atonement involved the high priest confessing the sins of the nation, while laying his hands on the head of a sacrificial goat</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:40-Lev26:42\">LEV 26:40–26:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:33-1Kgs8:36\">1KI 8:33–8:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:24-2Chr6:27\">2CH 6:24–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:46-1Kgs8:52\">1KI 8:46–8:52</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:36-2Chr6:39\">2CH 6:36–6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:5\">PSA 32:3–32:5</a></p>\n<h3>Under the new covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8-1John1:10\">1JN 1:8–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:13-Jas5:16\">JAS 5:13–5:16</a></p>\n<h2>Confession of sin accompanied by acts appropriate to repentance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:5-Num5:8\">NUM 5:5–5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:5-Lev5:6\">LEV 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:10-Ezra10:11\">EZR 10:10–10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:1-Neh9:3\">NEH 9:1–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:18-Acts19:19\">ACT 19:18–19:19</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of confession of sin</h2>\n<h3>On behalf of the nation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:5-Neh1:7\">NEH 1:5–1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:5-Ezra9:15\">EZR 9:5–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:12-Isa59:13\">ISA 59:12–59:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:6-Isa64:7\">ISA 64:6–64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:7\">JER 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:20\">JER 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:14\">DAN 9:4–9:14</a></p>\n<h3>By the people as a whole</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:5-1Sam7:6\">1SA 7:5–7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:4-Ezra9:7\">EZR 9:4–9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:10-Ezra9:15\">EZR 9:10–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:33-Neh9:35\">NEH 9:33–9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:6\">PSA 106:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:24-Jer3:25\">JER 3:24–3:25</a></p>\n<h3>By individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1-Ps51:5\">PSA 51:1–51:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:10\">2SA 24:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:10\">1CH 21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:17\">2SA 24:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:17\">1CH 21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:20\">JOB 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:5-Job42:6\">JOB 42:5–42:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></p>\n<h2>Confession of sin to other people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:20-Josh7:21\">JOS 7:20–7:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:17-Luke15:24\">LUK 15:17–15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a></p>",
